CVSS v3.1 Manual Calculation - VULN-001
========================================

Metric Values:
- AV: Network = 0.85
- AC: Low = 0.77
- PR: None = 0.85
- UI: None = 0.85
- S: Unchanged
- C: High = 0.56
- I: High = 0.56
- A: High = 0.56

Exploitability = 8.22 × AV × AC × PR × UI
Impact (Unchanged) = 6.42 × (1 - [(1-C) × (1-I) × (1-A)])
Base Score = Roundup(min(Impact + Exploitability, 10))

Calculate the final score and severity rating.
