Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: CVSS scores don't match online calculators

Verify you're using CVSS v3.1 (not v2.0 or v3.0)
Check that Privileges Required uses correct values for Changed scope
Ensure proper rounding (ceiling function for final score)
Issue: JSON parsing errors

Validate JSON syntax using python3 -m json.tool file.json
Check for missing commas or quotes
Ensure proper UTF-8 encoding
Issue: Import errors in Python scripts

Verify scripts are in correct directory
Use relative imports or add to PYTHONPATH
Check file permissions with ls -l
Issue: Incorrect severity ratings

Review severity thresholds (Critical: 9.0-10.0, High: 7.0-8.9, etc.)
Verify base score calculation before severity assignment
Check for off-by-one errors in range comparisons
